ComfyUI X-Dub

Portions of this project under xdub_runtime/source are derived from
KlingAIResearch/X-Dub:
https://github.com/KlingAIResearch/X-Dub

The upstream X-Dub code is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
Modifications in this distribution include an ONNX-based DWPose preprocessing
path, a ComfyUI node wrapper, and an isolated subprocess runtime integration.

X-Dub's inference framework is adapted from DiffSynth-Studio, and its public
model is based on Wan2.2. See README.md for project links and attribution.
